<h2 id="4-aesadvanced-encryption-standard">4. AES(Advanced Encryption Standard)</h2>
<ul>
  <li>AES(Advanced Encryption Standard)
    <ul>
      <li>Rijindael μ•κ³ λ¦¬μ¦</li>
    </ul>

    <p><img src="/assets/images/posts/SubstitutionPermutationNetwork2.png" alt="SPN" /></p>

    <p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Substitution%E2%80%93permutation_network">μ΄λ―Έμ§€ μ¶μ²</a></p>

